---
import DefaultLayout from '../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
import Feature from '../components/Feature.astro'
import CallToAction from '../components/CallToAction.astro'

---

<DefaultLayout title="Features">


  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="mb-16 text-6xl">
        Features of Laravel Mail
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-12 text-lg text-white-700">
        Laravel Mail is a powerful platform designed to simplify email marketing with advanced features like multi-SMTP support, email verification, and detailed message tracking. Perfect for businesses looking to scale their email outreach effectively.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <Feature icon="mdi:tailwind" title="Multiple SMTPs">
          Integrate seamlessly with popular SMTP providers such as Mailgun, SendGrid, Postmark, Amazon SES, and Zepto Mail. Manage multiple email services effortlessly.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:wheelchair-accessibility" title="Email Verification">
          Our platform includes a robust <b>self-hosted email verification</b> service to validate email addresses and reduce bounce rates. For example, a campaign sent to 75 subscribers experienced only two soft bounces.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:looks" title="Multiple Workspaces">
          Easily manage multiple workspaces or teams from a single, user-friendly interface, streamlining collaboration and organization.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:eslint" title="Golang MTA">
          Leverage our Multi server Go-based Mail Transfer Agent (MTA) to deliver millions of emails daily, ensuring high reliability and performance.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:eslint" title="Message Tracking">
          Gain valuable insights with advanced analytics, tracking email delivery, opens, clicks, bounces, and unsubscribes. Our built-in message tracking surpasses SendPortal's capabilities.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:theme-light-dark" title="Extensive Email Templates">
          Access over 1,000 pre-designed email templates imported from Unlayer.com. Simplify your email campaigns with ready-to-use, customizable designs.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:cog" title="Workflows and Automation">
          Create efficient email marketing workflows to grow your business faster. Our platform supports integrations with WordPress, Magento, and Shopify. Additional workflow automation can be customized using Laravel.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="mdi:cog" title="Asterix Integration">
          At release 0.5 we have will added basic Asterix to our platform. Asterix is a powerful IPBX solution to manage and host your own Voip solution.
        </Feature>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>



  <CallToAction />

</DefaultLayout>
